  "read_only_context_after": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00206:45d1df8bf1af]]",
  "read_only_context_before": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00192:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n设船到岸的垂直距离为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P00193:95d5a728bcb3]]，光束与岸边夹角为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P00194:2182836b0dd3]]，则沿岸距离[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00195:170a809b5188]]，探照灯角速度为\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P00196:f73e89ca97aa]] \n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P00197:4120f4119111]] \n当 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P00198:04778c61bd0c]] 时，\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P00199:46d0709c371e]] \n因此光点沿岸移动的速度约为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P00200:72e707fb7ffe]]。光点速度可以远大于船上灯头边缘的线速度，因为它是远处交点的几何扫掠速度；这里不能把 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P00201:f8cbed864bcf]] 里的 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P00202:c2bd0fa9eafa]] 直接取为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P00203:c8151cdc41bf]]，而要先写清光线与岸的交点位置。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00204:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}",
